txt.en: There are crawlers infesting Nan Tornaeth, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Nan Tornaeth, you should purge as many of the foul flesh-eating crawlers infesting the ruins as you can.
Crawlers infesting the gullies and cliffs of Nan Tornaeth are drawn to the rotting flesh of the wights which have arisen there.
